who remains with <b>his master</b>, the Archon Mardeus N`Vidi. <b>Find this priest</b> who wanders through the haunting, bathing in his own tainted <b>madness</b> and <b>relieve him of his existence</b>. <b>Upon his person</b> you shall find an incantation of blood. Return this to me, along with the eye of a Ravenous Abhorrent and the blood talon of a Bloodbone Drake; both creatures which you will find dwelling within the Haunting.'<br>
<br>
I'm surprised of the 168 people farming the phat lewtz in Rathe Mtns. earlier today only a couple bothered to spend more then 20 seconds reading his text =)<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ubalise.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Balise</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/1/01 1:37:39 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Silly people, tis not the Archon's blood he seeks...</span><hr size=1> We killed many of the madened priests and got nothing but cash from their corpses. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ufatal67.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Fatal67</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/1/01 2:51:57 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Silly people, tis not the Archon's blood he seeks...</span><hr size=1> You got cash? If you dont loot this mob in 30 seconds it poofs. Nothing. not even a copper.<br>
<br>
I did read the quest. Does that mean you can;t kill the Archon?<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ufreonsmurf.showPublicProfile?language=EN>FreonSmurf</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_star.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/1/01 4:42:41 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Silly people, tis not the Archon's blood he seeks...</span><hr size=1> Killed Archon, 40 min fight 30 ppl. No drops.<br>
