<br>
And to my understanding this Haunting is occuring in other zones as well? So perhaps looking outside of rm would be a good start. Either that or Verant overlooked adding the blood to the madman's table, much like the original Primordial Malice quest involving Izera N'kar was broken from the get-go <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ujaraan.showPublicProfile?language=EN>jaraan</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/1/01 2:11:16 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Silly people, tis not the Archon's blood he seeks...</span><hr size=1> Did this last night with my guildmates. After killing Archon which took about an hour with some 20 or so peeps, more coming to our aid after about half hour, nothing was on him. So we were looking for maddened priests as well. While roaming around looking for the priests, I noticed that 1) they con dubious, 2) were fighting all of the other mobs (ravenous abhorrent, etc). Did anyond tried to talk to the priests before killing them? I wanted to try but since there was like 100+ or so peeps in the zone, was hard to track him down before others killed him.<br>
<br>
