om/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/2/01 12:30:46 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Silly people, tis not the Archon's blood he seeks...</span><hr size=1> I escorted a priest around the zone today for about an hour ..<br>
